snippet.textDisplay: Today, I am feeling incredibly proud as the Sindhi culture and language are finally receiving the respect they deserve. As a fellow Sindhi from Larkana, I have been eagerly anticipating this moment on the Coke Studio platform. In Pakistani cricket, Shahnawaz Dahani (a Sindhi) has been given the opportunity to represent our country, while Ali Gul Mallah (also Sindhi) has been cast in comedic roles in the drama Ishq Murshid. And now, we have a beautiful Sindhi song featured on our favorite musical platform, Coke Studio. I would like to express my appreciation to all those involved in making this possible.
